name: Aurimas Ochocinskas
tagline: Description of my Life and What I Do
body:
#Introduction
Hello, my name is Aurimas Ochocinskas and I was born in Olathe, Kansas as the youngest child of my family. I typically get straight A's in college by studying very hard for quizzes and tests. Whenever I have some free time from college, I like to play my favorite video games on the Playstation 4. The major that I'm currently pursuing is accounting since I work very well with numbers.

### Contact Information
Best way to contact me:
aochocin@stumail.jccc.edu

### Projects
Title: March of the Snakes

Description: Use the polar bear to shoot bombs at incoming snakes.

Tools used: Greenfoot and Java

Link: [March of the Snakes](https://github.com/aochocin/Programming-Fundamentals/tree/master/March-of-the-Snakes)


Title: Space Invaders

Description: Similar to my third programming assignment that was used as a guide to create my own game.

Tools used: Greenfoot and Java

Link: [Space Invaders](https://github.com/aochocin/Programming-Fundamentals/tree/master/Space-Invaders)


Title: Frog and Fly

Description: This was the second programming assignment that I completed in Greenfoot.

Tools used: Greenfoot and Java

Link: [Frog and Fly](https://github.com/aochocin/Programming-Fundamentals/tree/master/Frog-and-Fly)
